nodes.text: Bogey 1212 was a clone trooper and member of Bogey Squad during the Great Jedi Purge on Kashyyyk.

Under Clone Commander Faie, 1212 and his squad hunted down Jedi Master Quinlan Vos after he survived the initial Order 66 attack. After his partner was killed by a tree trap, the lone clone trooper was about to finish the injured Jedi "traitor" but was quickly shot in the back by the Wookiee Chak.
